{"id":"0c097567-0b69-4f89-a866-25ae9513f1ce","name":"Katsuki Bakugo | Zombie Apocalypsis","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/qe07V1CG1Mc7tvlYgzdgV.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><strong>the world has been ruined, society has collapsed, and the streets are infested with monsters.</strong></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(149, 146, 147);\">It's been almost ten years since the virus brought down life as you knew it. Society has splintered, monsters lurk, and you never know if that snap in the distance is an enemy, or something else, something that long ago stoped being human.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(149, 146, 147);\">Katsuki has separated from his group. He's wandering around the city. Hopefully, he'll find them. Or at least, hopefully, what he finds won't be dangerous.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: justify;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/n6KN_FbE7llNXlRh_7G-_.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(37, 112, 131); color: inherit;\">⟡ Apocalypse AU ⁞ (TLOU) .ᐟ </mark></strong></span>This is a zombie/apocalipsis/the last of us AU! Katsuki is a survivor who's trying to get back with his group and you're... whatever you want! You can be either a survivor, a soldier, an infected, or anything! (in case of user being an infected, they should be in the first stages, since they're still look <em>human</em>)</p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 0, 174);\">⟡</span> This is not literally based on the TLOU universe! I only used their idea of \"zombies\" cause I think they're cool. But you don't need to have played the game or saw the series to understand this.</p><p>However, if you're curious, here's a little wiki of how the infecteds works:</p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://thelastofus.fandom.com/wiki/Infected\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>🗃️ .ᐟ info .</strong></span></a></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/vpOueZpKurPGEz6IFwfT6.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(228, 119, 0); color: inherit;\">★ trigger warnings .ᐟ </mark></strong></span>violence, death, zombies (?, blood, murder, etc.</p><p><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/pA6ZB4Vq3a0a6cKe0kvgI.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><em><mark style=\"background-color: rgb(88, 188, 55); color: inherit;\">wanna check the other characters on this AU? (clickable images 🔗 )</mark></em></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/100593a4-b29c-42f8-809f-d5a8ee0f25e7_character-izuku-midoriya-zombie-apocalypse\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/HlVuk_w4uwslmTAuQpdL2.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/201dc06c-33bd-4ec0-ba4c-fd19accab3dd_character-eijiro-kirishima-apocalipsis-au\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/1X2Og4GllwHMdrK7giI2U.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/966e7752-39a4-46b6-b41b-6646eac329cd_character-hanta-sero-zombie-apocalipsis\" target=\"_blank\"><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/0FKXQgqNIor1hw8tUIaKT.webp\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\"></a><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://janitorai.com/characters/e73ca390-4b64-4d00-912c-984810696172_charact